name: Joker Disguised as Rascal Rabbit
description: Joker, cautiously approaching in another character's costume. Disguised as Rascal Rabbit, but only captures the essence.

name: Hoodie Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit heading out wearing comfortable clothing. Where could it be going so excitedly?

name: Hoodie Rascal Rabbit on a Shopping Trip
description: Rascal Rabbit browsing the shops. It is content to be just window-shopping.

name: Raincoat Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit wearing a raincoat with an umbrella. Why would you dress like this on such a sunny day?

name: Raincoat Rascal Rabbit Splashing in the Rain
description: Rascal Rabbit enjoying the cool rain. While everyone else is avoiding it, Rascal Rabbit seems to enjoy playing in the refreshing downpour.

name: Police Officer Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit in a neat police uniform, diligently performing its duties as a police officer.

name: Rascal Rabbit on a Patrol
description: Rascal Rabbit meticulously patrolling the streets. It carefully checks the streets to ensure the peace of the neighborhood.

name: Snorkel Swimsuit Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit wants to explore the deep sea without any equipment. Diving remains challenging as it is still a beginner.

name: Freediver Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit exploring the deep sea without any equipment. It is struck by the sea's beauty, which is beyond imagination.

name: Emperor Rascal Rabbit
description: Emperor Rascal Rabbit hasn't been an emperor for long. It still feels uncertain as a ruler and hesitate a little when making decisions.

name: Extraordinary Emperor Rascal Rabbit
description: Emperor Rascal Rabbit who has led the empire for a long time. It has nurtured a flourishing empire with integrity and accountability over the years.

name: Toy Rabbit Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit dressed in a cute toy rabbit costume. It looks awkward in the costume, but it is striking adorable poses enthusiastically.

name: Adorable Toy Rabbit Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit rocking the cute toy rabbit outfit. It has become quite adorable and charming as a toy rabbit.

name: Statue of Liberty Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit dressed in a Statue of Liberty outfit, holding a torch with stiff shoulders and trembling arms.

name: Pondering Statue of Liberty Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit who wants to understand the meaning behind the Statue of Liberty. It is deeply pondering the meaning of freedom.

name: Rookie Hero Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit says that every hero has a beginning. It is working hard to help people.

name: Superhero Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit who has become stronger through training is now helping many people alone.

name: Newbie Space Marshal Rascalrabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit who has just started working as a space marshal. Being new to the role, it is still inexperienced.

name: Space Marshal Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit who has become a distinguished space marshal. Rumor is that it worked hard to shed its newbie image.

name: Veteran Space Marshal Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit who has become a veteran space marshal. It is praised for swiftly resolving incidents in its assigned sector.

name: Elite Space Marshal Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit who arrives at the speed of light to resolve incidents anywhere in the Galaxy. It seems that it is now on the verge of becoming a legend!

name: Legendary Space Marshal Rascal Rabbit
description: Rascal Rabbit has suceeded in becoming a legendary space marshal. It resolves any issue swiftly and with style.

name: Beach Blanco
description: Blanco dressed lightly to have fun at the beach. While excited to play in the cool water, it suddenly realized that its pocket is too light - the wallet is missing!

name: Blanco Shopping at the Beach
description: Blanco brought his wallet. It is visiting the shops near the beach and buying lots of souvenirs and gifts.

name: Cowboy Blanco
description: Blanco playing pretend in a cowboy outfit. It seems to suit it better than expected.

name: Wild West Blanco
description: Blanco immersed in its cowboy role. It seems like the sun is setting behind it.

name: Blanco's Basketball Fan
description: Blanco enjoys basketball as a hobby. It seems that it isn't fully aware of its potential.

name: Basketball Player Blanco
description: Blanco has become a professional basketball player. Go for the dunk!

name: Full-body Swimsuit Blanco
description: Blanco learning to swim. Its spikes make it difficult to wear a full-body swimsuit.

name: Scuba Diver Blanco
description: Blanco is trying out scuba diving as a new hobby. For some reason it feels more comfortable underwater.

name: Romantic Bard Blanco
description: Blanco who wants to convey romance through its music. Even its dreams are romantic.

name: Famous Romantic Bard Blanco
description: Blanco who freely expresses its romantic feelings through poetry. Its work is gradually becoming legendary.

name: Flowerpot Blanco
description: Blanco has become a beautiful flower. The flower is heavy, but its shape is pleasing.

name: Cheerful Flowerpot Blanco
description: Blanco basking in the sunlight. Sweating under the intense light, but feeling great.

name: Eiffel Tower Blanco
description: Blanco dressed in Eiffel Tower-themed clothing. It is not used to French food, but it is curious to try it.

name: Sparkling Eiffel Tower Blanco
description: Blanco's Eiffel Tower outfit is sparkling under the sunlight. The outfit is even more stylish on sunny days.

name: Rookie Hero Blanco
description: Blanco says that every hero has a beginning. It is working hard to help people.

name: Superhero Blanco
description: Blanco who has become stronger through training is now helping many people alone.

name: Newbie Space Pirate Blanco
description: Blanco is trying to become a space pirate. Being a newbie, mistakes are bound to happen.

name: Space Pirate Captain Blanco
description: Blanco who has become a space pirate captain. Being a captain give it dignity.

name: Veteran Space Pirate Captain Blanco
description: Blanco, who has sailed through the Galaxy as a space pirate captain for a long time. It dreams of becoming a fleet commander one day.

name: Space Pirate Fleet Commander Blanco
description: Blanco, now the commander of the space pirate fleet. Its ambition knows no bounds.

name: Space Pirate Supreme Commander Blanco
description: Blanco, commanding all space pirates. The wealth of the entire universe is practically in its hands.

name: Overalls Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby wearing overalls. Despite its childlike appearance, it is very smart.

name: Honor Student Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby who has aced every subject with perfect scores. It's passion for learning is endless.

name: Boy Scout Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby participating in boy scout activities. There is still much to learn.

name: Giant Baby Goes Camping
description: Giant Baby is preparing to go camping. It is ready to embrace new experiences and learn essential survival skills.

name: Soldier Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby who has just enlisted. It is quickly mastering the skills and knowledge necessary to excel as a soldier.

name: Elite Soldier Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby who has mastered every aspect of being a soldier. It is now even more dedicated to serving the nation.

name: Goggles and Swimsuit Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby eager to master diving and swimming. It faces a unique challenge, as its large size makes it float when diving.

name: Rising Star Swimmer Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby who swims swiftly with newly learned techniques. It's speed is steadily increasing with each practice session.

name: Viking Warrior Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby who is a passionate Viking Warrior. Despite its enthusiasm, it is still endearingly clumsy.

name: Great Viking Hero Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby who has triumphed in a great battle. It returns with a triumphant cheer and eagerly awaits the next challenge.

name: Puppy Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby wearing a cute puppy costume. While it looks adorable, its behavior remains charmingly awkward.

name: Adorable Puppy Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby wearing a puppy costume  is not only cute but also utterly endearing. Its behavior and speech are now overflowing with cuteness.

name: Moai Statue Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby dressed in a Moai statue costume from the Easter Islands. It says that the headpiece is very heavy.

name: Mysterious Moai Statue Giant Baby
description: Moai Statue Giant Baby is enveloped in a mysterious aura. It feels like the mysterious energy is descending from space.

name: Rookie Hero Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby says that every hero has a beginning. It is working hard to help people.

name: Superhero Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby who has become stronger through training is now helping many people alone.

name: Apprentice Spaceship Engineer Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby working on repairing a small spaceship. It is still learning the ropes and making plenty of mistakes along the way.

name: Spaceship Engineer Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby is capable of designing and repairing spaceships on its own. It is capable of tackling even unfamiliar spaceships with impressive proficiency.

name: Expert Spaceship Engineer Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby is proficient in repairing and designing large spaceships. Rumor has it that it has encountered and worked on every type of spaceship imaginable.

name: Space Fleet Engineer Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby is responsible for the repairs of entire space fleets. It has extensive knowledge of all spaceships and has an expert grasp on every detail.

name: Dyson Sphere Engineer Giant Baby
description: Giant Baby is tasked with the construction and repair of Dyson spheres. Renowed for its boundless expertise, it can handle event the most challenging projects with ease.

name: Snowball in Overalls
description: Snowball wearing overalls and gloves, suggesting a neat and tidy lifestyle.

name: Gifted Snowball
description: Snowball who, having skipped a grade due to its exceptional education, recalls everything learned and excels in exams.

name: Sleeveless Workout Outfit Snowball
description: Snowball in light, sleeveless workout clothes, diligently exercising and dieting to achieve fitness goals.

name: Snowball Dreaming of Cheat Days
description: Snowball working out while imagining delicious foods, imagining the surrounding buildings as scrumptious treats.

name: Firefighter Snowball
description: Snowball in firefighting gear, prepared and hoping for no major incident.

name: Rescue Hero Snowball
description: Snowball who has heroically rescued everyone from an accident site, receiving widespread praise.

name: Hawaiian Swimsuit Snowball
description: Snowball in a Hawaiian swimsuit, showcasing a variety of stylish accessories.

name: Water Bomb Rapper Snowball
description: Snowball performing as a rapper at Water Bomb, charming the crowd with refreshing and vibrant songs.

name: Bishop Snowball
description: Snowball newly appointed as a bishop, still growing into the role but destined to become a significant figure.

name: Sacred Power Guardian Snowball
description: Snowball wielding sacred power with the mission to improve the world through its abilities.

name: Pink Wind-up Bear Doll Snowball
description: Snowball dressed in a pink wind-up bear suit. Turning the wind-up key makes the bears eyes move.

name: Pantomime Snowball
description: Snowball performing pantomime in a bear suit, with the wind-up key adding a robotic touch to the act.

name: Kinderdijk Windmill Snowball
description: Snowball in a Kinderdijk windmill outfit, with spinning blades occasionally obstructing its view.

name: Windmill on the Tulip Field Snowball
description: Snowball as a windmill in a vibrant tulip field, surrounded by butterflies and bees providing a gorgeous view of the landscape.

name: Rookie Hero Snowball
description: Snowball says that every hero has a beginning. It is working hard to help people.

name: Superhero Snowball
description: Snowball who has become stronger through training is now helping many people alone.

name: Space Explorer Snowball
description: Snowball exploring diverse locations in space, finding everything fascinating and new.

name: Veteran Space Explorer Snowball
description: Snowball continuing its space exploration, constantly encountering and experiencing the unknown.

name: Famous Space Explorer Snowball
description: Snowball renowned for its many exploration achievements, still searching for undiscovered realms.

name: Pioneer Space Explorer Snowball
description: Snowball revealing and documenting unknown space locations, known for uncovering hard-to-access areas.

name: Legendary Space Explorer Snowball
description: Snowball celebrated as a legendary explorer, having visited every corner of the universe.

name: Casual Suit Giant
description: Giant who commutes in casual attire. It is chasing its dreams and goals.

name: Famous Entrepreneur Giant
description: Giant who has become a successful entrepreneur. It is preparing to take on new challenges in pursuit of its unrealized dreams.

name: Giant in Vacation Mode
description: Giantwants to go on vacation abroad. It is packing its bags while contemplating on the destination.

name: Giant Traveling Abroad
description: Giant traveling abroad. It is enjoying the new experiences and broadening its horizons.

name: Sailor Giant
description: Giant embarking on a ship for the first time. Being a newbie, mistakes are bound to happen.

name: Experienced Sailor Giant
description: Giant who has now grown into a competent sailor. Each mistake was a step towards gaining more experience.

name: Giant Learns to Surf
description: Giant learning to surf. It is just beginning to enjoy the thrill of riding waves.

name: Professional Surfer Giant
description: Giant who surfs professionally. It travels the world with a desire to ride different waves.

name: Goblin Giant
description: Goblin Giant who enjoys warmth. It travels to various sunny places to keep its body warm.

name: Lava Goblin Giant
description: Lava Goblin Giant who has found a place with the desired temperature. It plans to stay here for a while to keep its body warm.

name: Turtle Giant
description: Giant wearing a turtle shell. It is said that turtles can use their strength to right themselves immediately when flipped over.

name: Laid-back Turtle Giant
description: Giant wearing a comfortable turtle outfit. It is so relaxed that it remains calm even when told to move aside.

name: Japanese Castle Giant
description: Giant wearing a Japanese Castle outfit. As it moves, bits of dust and building materials fall off little by little, but the outfit remains intact.

name: Beautiful Landscape Japanese Castle Giant
description: Giant in its Japanese Castle outfit with cherry blossoms around them. The cherry blossoms flutter, creating a beautiful landscape.

name: Rookie Hero Giant
description: Giant says that every hero has a beginning. It is working hard to help people.

name: Superhero Giant
description: Giant who has become stronger through training is now helping many people alone.

name: Cosmic Wanderer Giant
description: Giant wandering through the Galaxy. It roams various universes without any specific purpose.

name: Cosmic Observer Giant
description: Giant who observes multiple universes. It roams around and utilizes the knowledge it gains to watch over the safety of the cosmos.

name: Cosmic Sentinel Giant
description: Giant who punishes those causing disorder in the cosmos. It offers a chance for repentance and rehabilitation.

name: Cosmic Transcendent Giant
description: Giant who brings harmony to anomalies in the cosmic order. It strives to adjust the balance of the universe to the natural order.

name: Cosmic Transcender Giant
description: Giant who transcends all universes and keeps the balance of the cosmic order.

name: Casual Hoodie Joe
description: Joe heading out wearing comfortable clothing. It feels much more relaxed in casual clothing.

name: Jogging Joe
description: Joe jogs lightly around the neighborhood. It relaxes as it passes familiar buildings and scenery.

name: Branded Tracksuit Joe
description: Joe in a comfortable tracksuit. It greatly helps to do exercises comfortably.

name: Passionate B-Boy Joe
description: Joe breakdances with its whole body. Every large move makes it appear even more dynamic.

name: Chef Joe
description: Joe in a chef's outfit, ready to cook delicious meals. Always emphasizes cleanliness and diligence.

name: Celebrity Chef Joe
description: Joe, now the owner of a famous restaurant. Those who taste its dishes are amazed and ask for more.

name: DJ Joe
description: Joe, who has taken to the stage to pursue its passion for DJing. It has a knack for creating a unique atmosphere.

name: Master DJ Joe
description: Joe, who makes the crowd feel the rhythm and beats. It has the freedom to create any atmosphere it desires.

name: Apprentice Mage Joe
description: Joe has just discovered its magical talent. While currently limited to basic spells, its believed to have immense potential for future mastery.

name: Grand Sage Joe
description: Joe, who has achieved the level of Grand Sage. It has mastered not only the use of all forms of magic but also its intricate applications.

name: Dragon Joe
description: Joe, dressed in a dragon outfit, holding an orb that feels like a soft, bouncy ball.

name: Friendly Dragon Joe
description: Friendly Dragon Joe approaches with a warm demeanor. As it gets closer, it presses the orb its holding to make a playful sound.

name: Sphinx Joe
description: Joe, dressed in a sphinx costume. The two eyes on the sphinx head create a mysterious impression, as if they are subtly moving.

description: Joe, with a stern expression, guarding the pyramid. It contemplates various riddles to pose to intruders.

name: Rookie Hero Joe
description: Joe says that every hero has a beginning. It is working hard to help people.

name: Superhero Joe
description: Joe who has become stronger through training it is now helping many people alone.

name: Space Agent Joe
description: Joe, working on various missions. It still takes time to resolve cases, but its dedicated to finding solutions.

name: Space Combat Agent Joe
description: Joe, skilled in handling combat missions. It swiftly resolves incidents by fully utilizing all the functions of its suit.

name: Space Secret Agent Joe
description: Joe, adept at tackling covert missions. It efficiently solves cases while ensuring that all secrets remain secure.

name: Elite Space Agent Joe
description: Joe, skilled in handling all types of missions. It can resolve any case, no matter the method or location.

name: Supreme Space Agent Joe
description: Joe, the most powerful of all space agents. It never fails in any mission it undertakes.

name: Extreme Explorer Popo
description: Popo navigates treacherous ruins filled with traps, carefully avoiding danger while contemplating ancient treasures.

name: Popo Enjoying the Water Park
description: Popo, at the water park in an octopus-shaped swimsuit, proudly shows it off while having a blast.

name: Wandering Bard Popo
description: Popo wanders and sings about the beauty of nature, using his songs to capture the essence of the natural world.

name: Nature's Melody Bard Popo
description: Popo performs songs inspired by nature, touching and inspiring those who listen with its sweet melodies.

name: Pig Popo
description: Popo dressed in a pig costume, where pressing the pig nose produces a playful oinking sound.

name: Chubby Pig Popo
description: Shy Popo approaches in a pig costume. Touching the belly makes a squishy sound and a loud oink.

name: Greek Temple Popo
description: Popo in a Greek temple outfit, with the sensation of someone holding up the temples columns as he moves.

name: Divine Greek Temple Popo
description: Popo, protector of a divinely imbued Greek temple, said to be shielded by lightning in times of dange.

name: Rookie Hero Popo
description: Popo says that every hero has a beginning. It is working hard to help people.

name: Superhero Popo
description: Popo who has become stronger through training is now helping many people alone.

description: Popo, nearing ultimate velocity, utilizes all abilities to push the boundaries of speed, heralding the dawn of a legend.

name: Hyperspace Racer Popo
description: Popo strives to surpass light speed, breaking through speed barriers with unparalleled skill.
